I will quote also a formulary for the reciting of the diptychs according to the use of an Irish Chureh. It is to be found in the Stowe Missal, inserted in the middle of the Memento of the dead used in the Roman Mass.³

Oum4 omnibus in toto mundo offerentibus sacrificium spiritale Deo Patri et Filio et Spiritui sancto sanetis ac venerabilibus sacerdotibus,

ut nomen domni Papae quicumque sedi apostolicae praefuerit, in nostris ecclesiis recitetur.'’
